name: Tunnelling
description:
You're a tiny quantum particle trying to catch some energy in a not so empty dark space.

You move with arrow keys, and you can due to the fact of being a quantum particle, you can do quantum tunnelling using space bar.

Yellow energy sparks let you score points.

Red energy sparks give you infinite quantum tunnelling power!

With a mouse click you can even change the world!
